{"tid":2132924,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民建聯前區議員助登記選民 7旬婦住址涉被種票驚現4不知名選民","createTime":"2020-07-30T16:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T17:36:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"66494767f285f2f3c871db1bb045987a76c8959c","tid":2132924,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/local/20200731/ON637FFDKFHQTGFLDV6QZYX6GE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FON637FFDKFHQTGFLDV6QZYX6GE%2F&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSs3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=68499754\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FON637FFDKFHQTGFLDV6QZYX6GE%2F&h=c0faeb13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/local/20200731/ON637FFDKFHQTGFLDV6QZYX6GE/</a><br />\n<br />\n民建聯捲「種票」疑雲！巿民馬先生向《蘋果》投訴，其居於筲箕灣的69歲母親（陳女士）去年區選前獲時任下耀東區議員、民建聯王志鍾上門派福袋，並向其母索取身份證資料和簽名，代為填寫選民登記表格，其母住址隨後收到4封非居於上址人士的選民登記確認信，其中一人更疑用地址借錢，導致有人上門貼大字報追債。馬先生就事件報警，質疑：「（民建聯）個福袋根本係利誘啲長者，其實係攞佢哋啲資料去種票！」王志鍾截稿前仍未回覆；一直協助馬先生的工黨區議員何偉倫指，選管會已將個案轉交執法機構跟進。"},{"pid":"57a6d4479f395474b740dd9317d3f88b7390f174","tid":2132924,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T16:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b04ef034f050d47384fe32fa0faccffbd163d5","tid":2132924,"uid":11291,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"DQ左咁多人仲要種票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共咪撚咁貪心啦"},{"pid":"432988378631900c744ee862c3d6b99adb9e40cd","tid":2132924,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike"